net.bytebuddy.description.enumeration

Interface EnumerationDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamedElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnumerationDescription.AbstractBase, EnumerationDescription.ForLoadedEnumeration, EnumerationDescription.Latent, TypePool.AbstractBase.RawEnumerationValue.LazyEnumerationDescription

    public interface EnumerationDescription
extends NamedElement
    Describes an enumeration value. Note that the Object.toString() method always returns the value as if the method was not overridden, i.e. the name of the enumeration constant.
